{"tid":730211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"無法！追查！","createTime":"2018-07-05T08:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T11:35:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"944f02e3b2cd3e6b0f286db63156cf65a29ae560","tid":730211,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:18:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180705/20440184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F20440184&d=joX5BlMYaDjyDY0d2WQwu8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=460ebecd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F20440184&h=57fd55fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180705/20440184</a><br />\n<br />\n無法！追查！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180705/large/1530698368_b58f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530698368_b58f.jpg&h=765f2d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n「有若干證據支持，但未能充份證明投訴屬實。」<br />\n<br />\n「無法追查。」<br />\n<br />\n港鐵高層唔使口窒窒，慌不擇路對記者說：「我會鼓勵xx出來交代一下。」大叔啊，你讀得書少嗎？鼓勵這兩個字，唔係咁用嘅！<br />\n與其對一直潛水、零回應、辦公室真空的主承建商離奇地跪着乞求，笑住包庇，希望他們開恩，心情好時，出來交代沙中綫的剪筋過程，倒不如，索性，向警隊學習，以上述文首的書面回應已離職的明報記者。<br />\n<br />\n連打到見血後腦需要縫針的警察施襲事故，也可以僅用22個中文字推卸晒所有刑責，這樣，港鐵剪了幾條筋，被分判商爆料，的確有若干證據支持，但未能充份證明投訴屬實，因為人在做，只有天在看，除了上帝，和上帝感召晚晚瞓得好的高層，和自貶智慧與能力處理唔到剪筋事故的局長，有乜責任要揹呢。<br />\n<br />\n明報記者後腦不是被旺角魚蛋襲擊，幾家傳媒有相有片，警方調查N個月，同場的梁天琦和其他街頭示威者已經被判暴動罪成，獲囚最高的盧建民坐七年監啊阿Sir。<br />\n<br />\n同一個旺角主場，市民被重判，警察被「無法追查」，市民是心眼雪亮的。由689與777打下的香港紅底江山，將會有更多「無法追查」。23條過關的話，「無法」升呢，未跪低的傳媒，還敢追查！  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n草莽英雄 (楊靜)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n解決土地問題&mdash;&mdash;填海 (尊子)"},{"pid":"7c78d994ac87c70aa1079bbe995768db0b12f8a3","tid":730211,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T08:46:09.000Z","msg":"無法可追踨的七對手<br />\n<br />\n帶出包庇永遠在背後"},{"pid":"c792131a20f7b09d3718e89124b95d8b984aabc6","tid":730211,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62109e5e77e115bc291cedf3291123a81d408198","tid":730211,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T11:35:50.000Z","msg":"傳媒既然有相有片，應該可以自己起底追查<br />\n再籌錢向警務署民事申訴，可行嗎？"}]}